  18,58,"wrbk alghafur ldhnwb eibadih 'iidha tabu, dhu alrahmat bhm, law yeaqb hwla' almerdyn ean ayatih bima kasabuu min aldhunub walatham lejjal lahum aledhab, wlknh taealaa halim la yueajil baleqwbt, bal lahum maweid yjazwn fih baemalhm, la mndwht lahum eanh wala mhyd"
