  19,12,"flma wld yhya, wabalagh mblghana yafham fih alkhitabi, 'amrih alllah 'an yakhudh altawrat bjdd wajthad bqwlh: ya yahyaa khudh altawrat bijidin wajthad bhfz alfazha, wafahm meanyha, waleamal bha, waetynah alhikmat wahusn alfhm, wahu saghir alsn"
  19,13,"watynah rahmatan wmhbt min eindina wthart min aldhnwb, wakan khayfana mtyeana lilah teala, mwdyana fraydh, mjtnbana mharmh"
  19,14,"wkan barrana biwalidayh mtyeana lhma, walam yakun mtkbrana ean taeat rbh, wala ean taeat waldyh, wala easyana lrbh, wala lwaldyh"
  19,15,"wslam min allah ealaa yahyaa wa'aman lah yawm wulid, wayawm ymwt, wayawm yubeth min qabrih hyana"
