  19,26,"fkly min alrtb, washrabi min alma' wtyby nfsana balmwlwd, fa'iina ra'ayt min alnaas ahdana fsalk ean amrk faquli lh: 'iiniy 'awjabt ealaa nafsi lilah skwtana, falan 'ukalim alyawm ahdana min alnaas. walskwt kan tebdana fi shrehm, dun shryet muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
