  19,35,"ma kan lilah taealaa wala ylyq bih 'an yatakhidh min eibadih wkhalqh wldana, tnzzah wtqddas ean dhlk, 'iidha qadaa amrana min al'umur waradh, sghyrana 'aw kbyrana, lm ymtne elyh, wa'iinama yaqul lh: \"kn\", fayakun kama sha'h waradh"
