  19,41,"wadhkur - 'ayuha alrasul - lqwmk fi hadha alquran qisat 'iibrahim - ealayh alslam - 'iinah kan eazim alsdq, wmin arfe 'anbia' allah taealaa mnzlt"
  19,42,"'idh qal li'abih azr: ya 'abat li'ayi shay' taebud min al'asnam ma la yasmae wala ybsr, wala yadfae eank shyyana min dun allh?"
  19,43,"ya abt, 'iina allah 'aetani min aleilm ma lam yetk, fa'aqbal mny, watbeny 'iilaa ma adewk 'ilyh, arshdk 'iilaa altariq alsawii aldhy la tdll fyh"
