  20,77,"wlqd 'awhayna 'iilaa mwsa: 'an akhruj laylana bieibadi min bani 'iisrayiyl min \"msr\", fattikhidh lahum fi albahr tryqana yabsana, laa takhaf min fireawn wajunuduh 'ana ylhqwkm fydrkwkm, wala takhshaa fi albahr ghrqana"
