  23,5,waldhyn hum lifurujihim hafizun mimaa hrram allah min alzna wallwat wakulu alfwahsh
  23,6,"'ila ealaa zwjathm 'aw ma malakat 'aymanuhum min al'ima', fala lwm ealayhim wala haraj fi jmaehn walastmtae bhn; li'ana allah taealaa ahllahn"
  23,7,"faman talab altmte bighayr zawjatih 'aw amatih fahu min almjawzyn alhlal 'iilaa alhram, waqad errad nafsih leqab allah wskhth"
  23,8,"waldhyn hum hafizun likuli ma awtmnu elyh, mwffun bikuli ehwdhm"
  23,9,"waldhyn hum ydawmwn ealaa 'ada' salatihim fi awqatha ealaa hyytha almshrwet, alwaridat ean alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm"
