  23,96,"'idha 'asa' 'iilayk aedawk - 'ayuha alrasul - bialqawl 'aw alfiel fala tqablhm bal'isa't, wlkn adfae 'isa'thm bal'ihsan mink 'ilyhm, nahn 'aelam bima ysfh hwla' almushrikun min alshirk waltkdhyb, wsnjazyhm ealayh 'aswa aljza'"
