  23,112,"wyusal alashqya' fi alnar: kam bqytm fi aldunya min alsnyn? wakam dyaetm fiha min taeat allh?"
  23,113,"qaluu lihwl almawqif wshdt aledhab: bqyna fiha ywmana 'aw baed ywm, fas'al alhussab aladhin yeddun alshuhur walayam"
  23,114,"qal lhm: ma labithtum 'iilaa wqtana qalilana law sabartum fih ealaa taeat allah lfztm baljnt, law kan eindakum eilm bdhlk; wdhlk li'ana mdt mkthhm fi aldunya qalilat jiddaan balnsbt 'iilaa tul mudatihim khalidin fi alnar"
