  23,116,"fteala allah almulk almtsrf fi kl shy', aldhy hu hq, wwedh hq, wweydh hq, wakulu shay' minh hq, wtaqaddas ean 'ana yakhluq shyyana ebthana 'aw sfhana, la 'ilh ghyrh rbb alersh alkrymi, aldhy hu 'aezam almkhlwqat"
